# Vulnerabilities in the AWS Lambda Node.js base image runtime itself.
# These are NOT in our application code — they live inside the base image's
# bundled npm installation and cannot be patched by us.
# Re-evaluate when AWS releases an updated Lambda Node.js 24 base image.

# undici DoS via unbounded WebSocket memory growth — in Lambda runtime npm
CVE-2026-12151

# ws DoS — in Lambda runtime npm
CVE-2026-48779
